Interface NetworkedContentManager.NetworkListener

Enclosing class:
NetworkedContentManager
public static interface NetworkedContentManager.NetworkListener

The listener interface for receiving network events. The class that is interested in processing a network event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addNetworkListener method. When the network event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.

See Also:
NetworkEvent
